OL,3,CFormer pupil at top NI school awarded
OL,4,Cdamages over school tour 'hazing'
OL,6,FMr McConkey, 19, sued the school's
OL,7,Fgovernors for alleged negligence and
OL,8,Ffailure to properly supervise the
OL,9,Fsenior rugby squad on the trip in
OL,10,FDecember 2022.
OL,12,FIn court on Wednesday, it was
OL,13,Fannounced that he is to be paid
OL,14,F#52,760 plus legal costs.
OL,16,FMr McConkey's family and solicitor
OL,17,Fdeclared the outcome a vindication in
OL,18,Ftaking the case.
