OL,6,FHis mother, Sian Mawhinney, said: "The
OL,7,Fchild that we sent on a school trip is
OL,8,Fnot the child that returned home to
OL,9,Fus, either physically or mentally.
OL,11,F"He looked absolutely broken by what
OL,12,Fhappened and what he witnessed."
OL,14,FMr McConkey, from the Carryduff on the
OL,15,Foutskirts of Belfast, was aged 17 and
OL,16,Fin Lower Sixth Form at Methody when
OL,17,Fselected to travel to a sports resort
OL,18,Fon the Algarve for warm weather
OL,19,Ftraining.
