OL,4,Cdamages over school tour 'hazing'
OL,6,FHe alleged that older pupils subjected
OL,7,Fhim and some of the other younger
OL,8,Fmembers of the squad to a series of so-
OL,9,Fcalled hazing incidents.
OL,11,FAccording to the statement of claim,
OL,12,Fhe was coerced into having his head
OL,13,Fshaved as part of humiliating rituals.
OL,15,FMr McConkey was also forced to strip
OL,16,Foff, run along a stretch of path and
OL,17,Fjump into a swimming pool in a "naked
OL,18,Fmile" ritual, it was alleged.
