OL,6,FHis lawyers contended that a further
OL,7,Fincident involved being made to
OL,8,Fwitness other pupils perform acts on a
OL,9,Fsex toy while allegedly wearing
OL,10,Fwomen's underwear.
OL,12,FProceedings were issued against the
OL,13,Fschool's board of governors for
OL,14,Falleged failures to prevent the hazing
OL,15,Fepisodes and to properly supervise
OL,16,Fpupils on the rugby tour.
OL,18,FThe action was listed for a three day
OL,19,Ftrial, but Mr Justice Fowler was
OL,20,Finformed that the settlement had been
OL,21,Freached on the terms disclosed.
