OL,6,FMr McConkey, who is now studying
OL,7,Fsports coaching at Gloucestershire
OL,8,FUniversity, attended court with his
OL,9,Ffamily for the outcome.
OL,11,FHis mother recalled him being "in a
OL,12,Fstate of trauma" following the trip.
OL,14,F"As a result of all this Gabriel left
OL,15,Fschool rugby because of the
OL,16,Fenvironment," she said.
